## API Endpoints

### GET /api/features

Получает список всех features

**Response:**

```json
{
  "features": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "title": "Feature title",
      "description": "Description",
      "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "userId": "user-1"
    }
  ]
}
```

### POST /api/features

Создает новую feature

**Request:**

```json
{
  "title": "Feature title",
  "description": "Description"
}
```

**Response:**

```json
{
  "feature": { /* feature object */ }
}
```

## State Management

Используется Zustand store: `useFeatureStore`

**Селекторы:**

```tsx
const features = useFeatureStore((state) => state.features)
const isLoading = useFeatureStore((state) => state.isLoading)
```

**Actions:**

```tsx
const { fetchFeatures, createFeature } = useFeatureStore()
```

